POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (02): WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1 ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES (AFGHANISTAN), CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1, ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS (DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO) ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES (MADAGASCAR): CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2, ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS (ALGERIA, CENTRAL AFRICAN REPUBLIC, DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO) ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES (SUDAN): PAKISTAN VIOLENCE
